name: Feeding frenzy (itch) (jenkgames)
description:
Feedign frenzy was made in about 3 hours for Friday Night Game Jam - #2022-38.

It is a game where you must survive by eating. Sounds simple right? However, you are not the only hungry fish in the aquarium. Can you out-eat your compatitors? Can you survive? (The game has no end so probably not)

Hope you enjoy the frenzy!

Controls: 

The game can only be playerd with WASD and space. These controls are: 

WASD to move around

and 

Space to eat.

Currently the hitbox used for eating is kind of small, so eating is not that simple. 

Anyway, good luck!
